osis-uk.org\u002Fsites\u002Fdefault\u002Ffiles\u002Ffiles\u002FInformation\u002FUnderstanding-endometriosis.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"\u003Eis the spleen.\u003C\u002Fa\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E Symptoms include severe, sometimes debilitating, pelvic pain, fatigue and heavy periods.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E"},"cardType":"Body","iFrameType":"","id":"future\u002Farticle\u002F20190116-what-is-endometriosis-0"},{"bodyHtml":{"assets":[]},"cardType":"Image","iFrameType":"","image":["p06y98yn"],"imageAlignment":"centre","id":"future\u002Farticle\u002F20190116-what-is-endometriosis-1"},{"bodyHtml":{"assets":[],"html":"\u003Cp\u003EWhile there are many lesser-known health conditions which are underfunded and under-researched, few are as common as endometriosis, which \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.endometriosis-uk.org\u002Fendometriosis-facts-and-figures\" target=\"_blank\"\u003Eaffects about 176m people globally\u003C\u002Fa\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E. In the US, where, as in other countries, \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.acog.org\u002F-\u002Fmedia\u002FFor-Patients\u002Ffaq013.pdf?dmc=1&amp;ts=20190107T1628367163\" target=\"_blank\"\u003Eit&rsquo;s estimated to affect one in 10 women of reproductive age\u003C\u002Fa\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E, \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Freport.nih.gov\u002Fcategorical_spending.aspx\" target=\"_blank\"\u003Eit receives about $6m (&pound;4.7m) in research funding each year\u003C\u002Fa\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E. Sleep research alone receives more than 50 times that amount.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003EMore in the&nbsp;\u003C\u002Fem\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fwww.bbc.com\u002Ffuture\u002Fcolumns\u002Fhealth-gap\" target=\"_blank\"\u003EHealth Gap\u003C\u002Fa\u003E\u003C\u002Fem\u003E\u003Cem\u003E:\u003C\u002Fem\u003E\u003Cbr \u002F\u003E&bull; \u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fwww.bbc.com\u002Ffuture\u002Fstory\u002F20180717-the-pelvic-floo