p in an urgent care centre. I&rsquo;d been Googling the different causes and one was endometriosis and I did suggest this to the doctor at the time and they just said, &lsquo;Oh no, it definitely isn&rsquo;t that&rsquo;,&rdquo; she says. &ldquo;I explained that I had really bad period pain and general abdomen pain and they still said no.&rdquo;\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOxford&rsquo;s Vincent isn&rsquo;t hesitant about whether gender plays a role. &ldquo;If every 14-year-old boy went to the GP saying, &lsquo;I miss two days of school every month&rsquo;, they would stop missing school every month,&rdquo; she says.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E"},"cardType":"Body","iFrameType":"","id":"future\u002Farticle\u002F20190116-what-is-endometriosis-12"},{"bodyHtml":{"assets":[]},"cardType":"Image","iFrameType":"","image":["p06y972s"],"imageAlignment":"centre","id":"future\u002Farticle\u002F20190116-what-is-endometriosis-13"},{"bodyHtml":{"assets":[],"html":"\u003Cp\u003EMaking matters more complicated, physicians also sometimes fail to find evidence of lesions on initial scans, \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\u002Fpmc\u002Farticles\u002FPMC2880548\u002F\" target=\"_blank\"\u003Eparticularly if the lesions are superficial\u003C\u002Fa\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E. Endometriosis forums are littered with \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fhealthunlocked.com\u002Fendometriosis-uk\u002Fposts\u002F135147208\u002Fnegative-ultrasound\" target=\"_blank\"\u003Estories of false negative ultrasound scans\u003C\u002Fa\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003EA lack of awareness on the patient side can delay diagnosis too. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\u002Fpmc\u002Farticles\u002FPMC4463372\u002F\" target=\"_blank\"\u003EMenstrual taboos still persist\u003C\u002Fa\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E and two of the women I spoke to reported being told, whether by family or through sexual educatio