rsquo;s health at the Royal College of GPs. Lone Hummelshoj, chief executive of the World Endometriosis Society, adds that the lack of specialist centres is another worldwide problem.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENo quick fix\u003C\u002Fstrong\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEven after a diagnosis is reached, symptom management is by no means straightforward &ndash;and misinformation persists here too.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E"},"cardType":"Body","iFrameType":"","id":"future\u002Farticle\u002F20190116-what-is-endometriosis-16"},{"bodyHtml":{"assets":[]},"cardType":"Image","iFrameType":"","image":["p06y97bt"],"imageAlignment":"centre","id":"future\u002Farticle\u002F20190116-what-is-endometriosis-17"},{"bodyHtml":{"assets":[],"html":"\u003Cp\u003ESome medical practitioners still tell patients pregnancy is an effective treatment. One physician this year told me she suspected endometriosis &ndash; but, she added, &ldquo;there&rsquo;s not much we can do unless you fancy getting pregnant&rdquo;. Given that the disease \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\u002Fpmc\u002Farticles\u002FPMC3538128\u002F\" target=\"_blank\"\u003Ecan impact fertility of patients\u003C\u002Fa\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E, this seems at the very least insensitive. It&rsquo;s also inaccurate: while it \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fendometriosis.org\u002Fresources\u002Farticles\u002Fendometriosis-and-pregnancy-breastfeeding\u002F\"\u003Emay relieve symptoms of endometriosis, \u003C\u002Fa\u003E\u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fendometriosis.org\u002Fresources\u002Farticles\u002Fendometriosis-and-pregnancy-breastfeeding\u002F\"\u003Eit&rsquo;s\u003C\u002Fa\u003E\u003Ca href=\"http:\u002F\u002Fendometriosis.org\u002Fresources\u002Farticles\u002Fendometriosis-and-pregnancy-breastfeeding\u002F\" target=\"_blank\"\u003E only for the duration of the pregnancy\u003C\u002Fa\u003E\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMeanwhil